@startuml
!theme plain

participant "User" as U
participant "Electron App" as EA
participant "File System" as FS
participant "AsyncWorker" as AW
participant "Redux Store" as RS
participant "Export Service" as ES
participant "Tracking Service" as TS
participant "Update Service" as US

U -> EA: Launch application
EA -> US: Check for updates
US --> EA: Update status

U -> EA: Load file system
EA -> FS: Read file system data
FS --> EA: Raw file system data
EA -> AW: Process data (hash, type, duplicates)
AW --> EA: Processed data
EA -> RS: Update state

U -> EA: Analyze data
EA -> RS: Retrieve data
RS --> EA: Current state
EA -> U: Display analysis

U -> EA: Export data
EA -> ES: Initiate export
ES -> AW: Process export (CSV, Excel, RESIP, etc.)
AW --> ES: Exported data
ES --> EA: Export complete
EA -> U: Provide export file

U -> EA: Perform action (edit metadata, tag, etc.)
EA -> RS: Update state
RS --> EA: Updated state
EA -> TS: Log user action

U -> EA: Close application
EA -> TS: Send usage data
EA -> US: Check for updates before exit

@enduml